"OB": "Currently, the search results are not being selected in the external jar.",

"SR": "To resolve this issue, please ensure that you have JDK1.3.1 set as the default JRE and that you have the source for rt.jar. Then, follow these steps:\n1. Open the java.io.File class.\n2. Search for the field 'tmpFir'.\n3. Verify that the search results are being correctly selected."}
